name: Delivery'sHIGH
description:
Downloadable games for Windows Story---------------

Operate the courier vehicle ACA-VO,
Avoid unfair enemy attacks and deliver a package
-----------------------------------

controller

Use the left and right keys only.
A-Jump
B-shot

keyboard

Use the left and right arrow keys only.
Z-jump
X-shot

Tips----------------

There are 9 levels.
1 level 30 seconds. After 30 seconds, the vehicle explodes and the reduce by one.
If you get an item on the title screen, the stock will increase to 99.

Game Engine ------------------

Pixel Game Maker MV
